{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>'LumineNight'</strong> is a <strong>mystery adventure game</strong> set in the city of Summerset, USA, in the 1950s. You can play as Detective Kelvin Foster and his only daughter, self-proclaimed Detective Selen Foster, to unravel the secrets of a series of unresolved murders over a decade. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players need to <strong>investigate</strong>, <strong>solve puzzles and codes</strong>, <strong>infiltrate</strong>, <strong>interrogate</strong>, and <strong>deduce the truth</strong>, all based on the following five <strong>detective principles:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>1. Find Clues in Dark Streets</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/001.gif?t=1733704380\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/002_eng.gif?t=1733704380\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In a corrupted city's darkness, the detective's eyes are the only thing you can trust.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the deep night, the neon-lit streets are filled with truths yet to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gathering raw evidence is the mother of all detective work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Detectives who pursue the truth <strong>prowl through the city</strong> in the night's darkness, <strong>gathering</strong> even the slightest clue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>2. Use All Your Senses to Unravel Tricks and Codes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/puzzle1.jpg?t=1733704380\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/nixie_puzzle.gif?t=1733704380\" /><strong>Nothing can stand in the way of those seeking the truth.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A piece of advice from a father to his daughter, a genius in deciphering codes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Riddles</strong> and <strong>puzzles</strong> encountered during the investigation, doors that are firmly locked and won't open, <strong>codes</strong> containing secrets that penetrate all truths...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything awaits the touch of a solver.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>3. Sneak among the Shadows</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/sneak_eng.gif?t=1733704380\" /><strong>As a detective, sometimes you should act before getting permission.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you secretly <strong>infiltrate</strong> and bypass strict security, you might be able to access <strong>crucial clues</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>4. Prove Contradictions Between the Crime Scene and Testimonies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/003_eng.gif?t=1733704380\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/reason2_eng.gif?t=1733704380\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If there are manipulated traces in the crime scene or testimonies that do not align, you can verify the contradicting aspects through interrogation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you refute the contradictions with your logic, the masks of those riddled with lies will be stripped away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>5. Complete the Deduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/005_eng.gif?t=1733704380\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544570/extras/006.gif?t=1733704380\" />You can <strong>deduce</strong> the beginning and end of all incidents, the reality behind secrets, and what each character wanted to hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Revealing the truth now <strong>depends upon you</strong>.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Investigation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/440589246108c6acd9203262050d390c2423a289.jpg"},{"name":"Robbery in Salty Mary Station","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/8c774a4c5bb8df70d6790c137b23ac53d9078d63.jpg"},{"name":"Invitation for UCDT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/1c3ce2e4cc5047927e89c2370cc7bb4e9a134a90.jpg"},{"name":"Unexpected Murder Case","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/082a9751d326cc243931d1fbd8cb56c4b12407bc.jpg"},{"name":"I had no choice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/f0b4b03b93da47de8c9fbd9941b10a38422284c4.jpg"},{"name":"A Curious Incident of a Mansion in the Nighttime","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/3ec5ebe7507d8187b65821e2911118ffd0347e58.jpg"},{"name":"The Mystery of Hotel Room 2805","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/79e74d1972506fd28f286cdf6d6b31ffda1630ab.jpg"},{"name":"The Woman Called Scarlett West","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/5db4377001fbacacf5d9de5bf7960320e51e381f.jpg"},{"name":"The Saint of the Alleyway","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544570/489187550f50af850654e367624caa035cc9054b.jpg"},{"name":"The Hour Bet